    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1930-07-03T10:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1930-07-03T10:00:00-05:00" n="337"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d337">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">715.1715/373: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Minister in Honduras</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Lay</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Tegucigalpa</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1930-07-03T09:00:00-06:00"
                            >July 3, 1930—9 a.m.</date>
                        <lb/>[Received 1 p.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>57. The draft protocol of agreement transmitted in Department’s instruction No. 1
                    of May 21 was submitted to the Honduran Government yesterday.</p>
                <p>Repeated to Managua.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Lay</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
